import React from 'react';
import {Typography,Grid, AppBar,CssBaseline ,Toolbar, Container } from '@mui/material'
import KeyboardArrowDownIcon from '@mui/icons-material/KeyboardArrowDown'; 
import SearchOutlinedIcon from '@mui/icons-material/SearchOutlined';
import { makeStyles } from '@mui/styles';
import logo from '../atoms/images/logo.png';
import Image from '../atoms/Image'
import User from '../atoms/User'
import Icons from '../atoms/Icons';

const useStyles = makeStyles(theme => ({
    avatar: {
      position: 'absolute',
      left:'125%', 
       },
    arrowUp:{
        height:'6.5px',
        width: '10.6px',
      color: 'black',
      position: 'absolute',
      left:'40.69%', top:'30%'
    },
    arrowDown:{
        height:'6.5px',
        width: '10.6px',
      color: 'black',
      position: 'absolute', 
    },
    search:{color: 'black',
    position: 'absolute',
    left: '8.33%',
    right: '7.03%',
    top: '8.33%',
    bottom: '7.03%',
    height:'20px',
    width: '20px',

    },
    logo:{position: 'absolute',
      left: '17.36%',
      right: '74.02%',
      top: '30.88%',
      bottom: '34.88%'
    },
  explore:{
      color: 'black',
      position: 'absolute',
      fontSize: '16px',
      fontStyle: 'normal',
      fontWeight: '500',
      lineHeight: '20px',
      letterSpacing: '0em',
      textAlign: 'left',
      top:'30%',
      height:'20px',
      width: '57px',
  },
  myLib:{
    color: 'black',
        position: 'absolute',
        left:'45.69%',
        fontSize: '16px',
        fontStyle: 'normal',
        fontWeight: '500',
        lineHeight: '20px',
        letterSpacing: '0em',
        textAlign: 'left',
        top:'30%'
  }
  })); 
interface Props{
    handleToggle?:any
}
const CustomAppbar=(props:Props)=>{
    const classes=useStyles()
    return (
        <>
        <CssBaseline />
    <AppBar  style={{ background: '#FFFFFF'}} position='relative' elevation={0}>
      <Toolbar>
          <Container style={{marginLeft:"13%", marginTop:'1%',}}>
            <Grid container >
                <Grid item md={2}>
                    <Image className={classes.logo} path={logo} />
                </Grid>

                <Grid item md={1}>
                    <Icons className={classes.search}>
                        <SearchOutlinedIcon/>
                    </Icons>
                </Grid>

                <Grid item md={1}>
                <Typography className={classes.explore} variant='body1'>Explore</Typography>
                </Grid>

                <Grid item md={1}>
                <KeyboardArrowDownIcon /* style={{ color: 'black',
                position: 'absolute',
                left:'31.69%', top:'30%'}} */ className={classes.arrowUp} onClick={(e)=>props.handleToggle(e,1)}/>
                </Grid>

                <Grid item md={1}>
                    <Typography className={classes.myLib} variant='body1' >My Library</Typography>
                </Grid>

                {<Grid item md={3}>
                </Grid>}

                <Grid item md={1}>
                    <User username="B" />
                   
                </Grid>

                <Grid item >
                <Icons>
                    <KeyboardArrowDownIcon className={classes.arrowDown} />
                    </Icons>
                </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Container>
      </Toolbar>
    
    </AppBar>
        </>
    );
}

export default CustomAppbar;
